## üåü Executive Summary
**Acoustix Pulse** is a cutting-edge, AI-driven healthcare ecosystem designed to provide accessible, rapid, and intelligent medical diagnostic support. By combining specialized machine learning models with state-of-the-art Large Language Models (LLMs) via **Amazon Bedrock**, the platform offers a comprehensive suite of tools ranging from respiratory sound analysis to complex cardiac risk assessment and medical image interpretation.

